{
  "video_id": "x7I5BWW-0c8",
  "title": "The warmth and wisdom of mud buildings | Anna Heringer",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12916.0,
      "end_time": 16273.0,
      "text": "It was the end of October in the mountains in Austria."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17262.0,
      "end_time": 20698.0,
      "text": "I was there on a field trip with my architecture students from Zurich."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21480.0,
      "end_time": 24846.0,
      "text": "And when we reached a high valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25619.0,
      "end_time": 28880.0,
      "text": "I surprised them with the news that there was no hut"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28112.0,
      "end_time": 29729.0,
      "text": "or hotel booked for the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31372.0,
      "end_time": 33390.0,
      "text": "It was not a mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33630.0,
      "end_time": 34951.0,
      "text": "It was totally on purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36913.0,
      "end_time": 40730.0,
      "text": "The challenge was to build our own shelter with whatever we could find."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42482.0,
      "end_time": 43874.0,
      "text": "And we all survived."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43898.0,
      "end_time": 46191.0,
      "text": "It was cold, it was really tough ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46842.0,
      "end_time": 49525.0,
      "text": "and it was a great learning experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49549.0,
      "end_time": 53359.0,
      "text": "to discover that there are a lot of resources given by nature for free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53383.0,
      "end_time": 57200.0,
      "text": "and all that we need is our sensitivity to see them ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58300.0,
      "end_time": 60300.0,
      "text": "and our creativity to use them."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62150.0,
      "end_time": 65236.0,
      "text": "I found myself in a similar situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66245.0,
      "end_time": 70746.0,
      "text": "When I was an architecture student about 13 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70770.0,
      "end_time": 74590.0,
      "text": "I went to Bangladesh to a remote village called Rudrapur"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 74830.0,
      "end_time": 77448.0,
      "text": "with the aim to design and build a school as my thesis project."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 81202.0,
      "text": "I had lived in that village before when I was 19 and a volunteer"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81227.0,
      "end_time": 84164.0,
      "text": "at Dipshikha, a Bangladeshi NGO for rural development."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84188.0,
      "end_time": 85870.0,
      "text": "And what I had learned from them"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85894.0,
      "end_time": 90672.0,
      "text": "was that the most sustainable strategy for sustainable development"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90696.0,
      "end_time": 95855.0,
      "text": "is to cherish and to use your very own resources and potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95879.0,
      "end_time": 99308.0,
      "text": "and not get dependent on external factors."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99332.0,
      "end_time": 102187.0,
      "text": "And this is what I tried to do with my architecture as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103179.0,
      "end_time": 106560.0,
      "text": "In terms of suitable building materials for my school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 106584.0,
      "end_time": 108120.0,
      "text": "I didn't have to look far."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108538.0,
      "end_time": 110393.0,
      "text": "They were right under my feet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111552.0,
      "end_time": 115407.0,
      "text": "mud, earth, dirt, clay, however you call it ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 116608.0,
      "end_time": 118941.0,
      "text": "and bamboo that was growing all around."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121220.0,
      "end_time": 125355.0,
      "text": "Electricity in remote Bangladesh is rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125379.0,
      "end_time": 126585.0,
      "text": "but we didn't need it."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126609.0,
      "end_time": 128208.0,
      "text": "We had human energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128232.0,
      "end_time": 130430.0,
      "text": "and the people were happy to have the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132800.0,
      "end_time": 133947.0,
      "text": "Tools were an issue, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 133971.0,
      "end_time": 135534.0,
      "text": "but we had these guys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135558.0,
      "end_time": 136986.0,
      "text": "water buffalos."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138550.0,
      "end_time": 140686.0,
      "text": "We had also tried a bit cows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140710.0,
      "end_time": 143289.0,
      "text": "but interestingly, they were too intelligent."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143830.0,
      "end_time": 146726.0,
      "text": "They were always stepping in the holes of the previous round."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 146750.0,
      "end_time": 148608.0,
      "text": "They wouldn't mix the mud, the straw --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148632.0,
      "end_time": 149682.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149706.0,
      "end_time": 152340.0,
      "text": "the sand, which are the ingredients in the walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153991.0,
      "end_time": 156365.0,
      "text": "And except a small team of consultants"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156389.0,
      "end_time": 158492.0,
      "text": "like my partner for realization, Eike Roswag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158516.0,
      "end_time": 161134.0,
      "text": "and my basket-weaver cousin, Emmanuel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161158.0,
      "end_time": 165516.0,
      "text": "it was all built by craftsmen from the village."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167433.0,
      "end_time": 170716.0,
      "text": "And this is the METI school after six months of construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 170741.0,
      "end_time": 173840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173108.0,
      "end_time": 174267.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174291.0,
      "end_time": 175893.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175917.0,
      "end_time": 180220.0,
      "text": "Load-bearing earth walls that really ground the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180460.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "and large bamboo structures that bring the lightness in."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185455.0,
      "end_time": 187876.0,
      "text": "That's the classroom on the ground floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188892.0,
      "end_time": 190662.0,
      "text": "Attached to it are the caves."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 191583.0,
      "end_time": 193997.0,
      "text": "They're for reading, for snuggling, for solo work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 194210.0,
      "end_time": 195662.0,
      "text": "for meditation, for playing ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196711.0,
      "end_time": 198464.0,
      "text": "and the classroom on the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201651.0,
      "end_time": 205434.0,
      "text": "The children all signed with their names in Bengali the doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 205458.0,
      "end_time": 208799.0,
      "text": "and they did not only sign, they also helped building the school."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210270.0,
      "end_time": 212928.0,
      "text": "And I'm sure you all had your hands in mud or clay before."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212953.0,
      "end_time": 214766.0,
      "text": "It's wonderful to touch. I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 214790.0,
      "end_time": 216130.0,
      "text": "The children loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216714.0,
      "end_time": 221569.0,
      "text": "And can you imagine the feeling of a small boy or a girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221593.0,
      "end_time": 225522.0,
      "text": "or an illiterate day laborer standing in front of that school building"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225546.0,
      "end_time": 227870.0,
      "text": "and knowing that you built this"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227111.0,
      "end_time": 230704.0,
      "text": "out of the ordinary bamboo and just the dirt underneath your feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 230729.0,
      "end_time": 233375.0,
      "text": "using nothing but your hands?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235381.0,
      "end_time": 241580.0,
      "text": "That gives such an enormous boost of trust and confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 241820.0,
      "end_time": 243970.0,
      "text": "in yourself and the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 244630.0,
      "end_time": 246114.0,
      "text": "And in the material."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 247168.0,
      "end_time": 250370.0,
      "text": "Especially mud has a very poor image."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 250610.0,
      "end_time": 253165.0,
      "text": "When we think of mud, we think of dirt --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253189.0,
      "end_time": 255403.0,
      "text": "it's ugly, it's nondurable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255427.0,
      "end_time": 257957.0,
      "text": "and this is the image I want to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 258978.0,
      "end_time": 262726.0,
      "text": "In fact, it's the 11th rainy season for this school now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 262750.0,
      "end_time": 266400.0,
      "text": "really harsh, horizontal monsoon rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266280.0,
      "end_time": 268575.0,
      "text": "and the walls are standing strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 268951.0,
      "end_time": 273460.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273484.0,
      "end_time": 274825.0,
      "text": "So how does it work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 274850.0,
      "end_time": 279600.0,
      "text": "First rule, a good foundation that keeps the wall dry from the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 279300.0,
      "end_time": 282726.0,
      "text": "and second rule, a good roof that protects from the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 282750.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "and third rule, erosion control."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 286130.0,
      "end_time": 288299.0,
      "text": "Mud walls need speed breakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 288323.0,
      "end_time": 292531.0,
      "text": "so that the rainwater cannot run down the wall fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 292555.0,
      "end_time": 295837.0,
      "text": "and these speed breakers could be lines of bamboo"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 295861.0,
      "end_time": 299442.0,
      "text": "or stones or straw mixed into the mud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 299466.0,
      "end_time": 304727.0,
      "text": "just like a hill needs trees or rocks in order to prevent erosion."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304751.0,
      "end_time": 306123.0,
      "text": "It works just the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 307160.0,
      "end_time": 311193.0,
      "text": "And people always ask me if I have to add cement to the mud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311217.0,
      "end_time": 312692.0,
      "text": "and the answer is no."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313131.0,
      "end_time": 316869.0,
      "text": "There is no stabilizer, no coating on these walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 316894.0,
      "end_time": 318218.0,
      "text": "only in the foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320114.0,
      "end_time": 321931.0,
      "text": "So this is the close-up of the wall"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 321956.0,
      "end_time": 325416.0,
      "text": "after 10 rainy seasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 325440.0,
      "end_time": 327880.0,
      "text": "and as much as I grew a bit older,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 327904.0,
      "end_time": 329626.0,
      "text": "the wall got some wrinkles as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 329650.0,
      "end_time": 331816.0,
      "text": "The edges my not be as sharp as before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 331841.0,
      "end_time": 333993.0,
      "text": "but it still looks pretty good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334170.0,
      "end_time": 335747.0,
      "text": "and if it needs repairing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 335771.0,
      "end_time": 337762.0,
      "text": "it is really easy to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 337786.0,
      "end_time": 339529.0,
      "text": "You just take the broken part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 339553.0,
      "end_time": 342291.0,
      "text": "make it wet, and put it back on the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 342315.0,
      "end_time": 344338.0,
      "text": "and it will look the same as before."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344362.0,
      "end_time": 345905.0,
      "text": "Wish that would work on me, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 345929.0,
      "end_time": 349229.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 350505.0,
      "end_time": 352661.0,
      "text": "Yeah, and the great thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 352685.0,
      "end_time": 355106.0,
      "text": "if an earth wall is not needed anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355130.0,
      "end_time": 358371.0,
      "text": "it can go back to the ground it came from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358395.0,
      "end_time": 360303.0,
      "text": "turn into a garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360327.0,
      "end_time": 363850.0,
      "text": "or get fully recycled without any loss of quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364427.0,
      "end_time": 366518.0,
      "text": "There's no other material that can do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366542.0,
      "end_time": 370866.0,
      "text": "and this is why mud is so excellent in terms of environmental performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 372241.0,
      "end_time": 374376.0,
      "text": "What about the economic sustainability?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 375720.0,
      "end_time": 376338.0,
      "text": "When we built the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 376362.0,
      "end_time": 378739.0,
      "text": "I practically lived on the construction site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 378763.0,
      "end_time": 381787.0,
      "text": "and in the evening, I used to go with the workers to the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 381811.0,
      "end_time": 383887.0,
      "text": "and I could see how they spent their money."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 384804.0,
      "end_time": 388104.0,
      "text": "And they would buy the vegetables from their neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388128.0,
      "end_time": 391413.0,
      "text": "they would get a new haircut or a new blouse from the tailor."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 392678.0,
      "end_time": 396536.0,
      "text": "And because the main part of the building budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 396560.0,
      "end_time": 398705.0,
      "text": "was spent on craftsmanship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 398729.0,
      "end_time": 401161.0,
      "text": "the school wasn't just a building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 401185.0,
      "end_time": 405349.0,
      "text": "it became a real catalyst for local development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 405373.0,
      "end_time": 406873.0,
      "text": "and that made me happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 408809.0,
      "end_time": 411207.0,
      "text": "If I had designed the school in cement and steel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 411231.0,
      "end_time": 414834.0,
      "text": "this money would have been exported and lost for those families."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 416334.0,
      "end_time": 420508.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 421755.0,
      "end_time": 425326.0,
      "text": "The building budget at that time was 35,000 euros --"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 425350.0,
      "end_time": 427311.0,
      "text": "it's probably doubled by now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 427335.0,
      "end_time": 430423.0,
      "text": "and this is a lot of money for that region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 430447.0,
      "end_time": 434452.0,
      "text": "and especially because this money is working within the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 434476.0,
      "end_time": 435754.0,
      "text": "and rotating fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 435778.0,
      "end_time": 437460.0,
      "text": "and not on the stock market."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438222.0,
      "end_time": 443790.0,
      "text": "So when it comes to the economic sustainability of my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 443103.0,
      "end_time": 446349.0,
      "text": "my main question is, who gets the profit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 448769.0,
      "end_time": 450786.0,
      "text": "How many of you in here"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 450810.0,
      "end_time": 452992.0,
      "text": "have some experience living in a mud house?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 453334.0,
      "end_time": 455371.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson, where is your hand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 455395.0,
      "end_time": 456452.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 456476.0,
      "end_time": 457650.0,
      "text": "You? OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 458959.0,
      "end_time": 460110.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 460134.0,
      "end_time": 463299.0,
      "text": "It seems totally out of our focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 463323.0,
      "end_time": 467957.0,
      "text": "but approximately three billion people all around the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 467981.0,
      "end_time": 470464.0,
      "text": "are living in earth houses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 470488.0,
      "end_time": 472774.0,
      "text": "and it is a traditional building material"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 472798.0,
      "end_time": 475511.0,
      "text": "in Europe just as much as in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 477896.0,
      "end_time": 479437.0,
      "text": "Strangely enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 479461.0,
      "end_time": 483126.0,
      "text": "mud is not considered worthy of being studied at universities ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 484101.0,
      "end_time": 487299.0,
      "text": "so I brought the dirt to Harvard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 487323.0,
      "end_time": 489530.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 489554.0,
      "end_time": 493530.0,
      "text": "precisely 60 tons of dirt right in front of the main facade"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 493554.0,
      "end_time": 495155.0,
      "text": "of the Graduate School of Design."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 497298.0,
      "end_time": 499442.0,
      "text": "Students and faculty rolled up their sleeves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 499466.0,
      "end_time": 500621.0,
      "text": "got their hands dirty"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 500645.0,
      "end_time": 504440.0,
      "text": "and transformed the front into a warm place for people to gather."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 505680.0,
      "end_time": 506784.0,
      "text": "Children would climb the structures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 506808.0,
      "end_time": 508325.0,
      "text": "skaters would ride the ramp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 508349.0,
      "end_time": 510940.0,
      "text": "students having lunch breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 510119.0,
      "end_time": 514191.0,
      "text": "and it was particularly fascinating to see how many people were touching the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 514215.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518680.00000000006,
      "text": "and we usually don't go around cities caressing our facades, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 518919.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519952.99999999994,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 524186.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526833.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 528423.0,
      "end_time": 530430.0,
      "text": "Of course, this was a small-scale project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 530454.0,
      "end_time": 533550.0,
      "text": "but in terms of awareness-building and in terms of education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 533574.0,
      "end_time": 536103.0,
      "text": "it was like an acupuncture trigger point."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537521.0,
      "end_time": 541101.0,
      "text": "And in fact, in more and more countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 541125.0,
      "end_time": 546110.0,
      "text": "load-bearing earthen structures are not allowed to be built anymore"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546134.0,
      "end_time": 549636.0,
      "text": "although they're traditional and have lasted for hundreds of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 549660.0,
      "end_time": 551675.0,
      "text": "and not because the material is weak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 551700.0,
      "end_time": 554852.0,
      "text": "but because there are no architects and engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 554876.0,
      "end_time": 557312.0,
      "text": "who know how to deal with that material."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 557336.0,
      "end_time": 559100.0,
      "text": "So education on all levels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 559340.0,
      "end_time": 561710.0,
      "text": "for craftsmen, engineers and architects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 561734.0,
      "end_time": 563501.0,
      "text": "is really strongly needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 563905.0,
      "end_time": 567249.0,
      "text": "Equally important is technological development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 567273.0,
      "end_time": 570366.0,
      "text": "like prefabrication developed by my colleague Martin Rauch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 570390.0,
      "end_time": 574376.0,
      "text": "who is an Austrian artist and expert in earthen structures."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 574400.0,
      "end_time": 578100.0,
      "text": "And he has created technologies for rammed earth elements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 578340.0,
      "end_time": 580467.0,
      "text": "for prefabrication of rammed earth elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 580491.0,
      "end_time": 584252.0,
      "text": "that include insulation, wall heatings and coolings"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 584276.0,
      "end_time": 586770.0,
      "text": "and all sorts of electrical fittings"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 586101.0,
      "end_time": 588394.0,
      "text": "that can be layered to multistoried buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 588418.0,
      "end_time": 591950.0,
      "text": "and this is important in order to scale up"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 591119.0,
      "end_time": 593870.0,
      "text": "and in order to fasten up the processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 593111.0,
      "end_time": 596411.0,
      "text": "like in the Ricola Herb Center in Switzerland."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 598375.0,
      "end_time": 601503.0,
      "text": "And finally, we need good built projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 601527.0,
      "end_time": 604622.0,
      "text": "that prove you can build with an ancient material"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 604646.0,
      "end_time": 606514.0,
      "text": "in a very modern way."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 607254.0,
      "end_time": 610948.0,
      "text": "It is not a matter of how old a material is;"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 610972.0,
      "end_time": 614453.0,
      "text": "it's a matter of our creative ability to use it today."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 616756.0,
      "end_time": 619110.0,
      "text": "These, for example, are three hostels"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 619350.0,
      "end_time": 621382.0,
      "text": "that I did in China in the village Baoxi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 621406.0,
      "end_time": 624191.0,
      "text": "about six hours by bus from Shanghai."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 625679.0,
      "end_time": 628370.0,
      "text": "The outside shape is woven bamboo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 628394.0,
      "end_time": 631957.0,
      "text": "and the inside core is stones and rammed earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 632878.0,
      "end_time": 635334.0,
      "text": "And it is a traditional building material."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 635358.0,
      "end_time": 637550.0,
      "text": "Even large parts of the Great Wall of China"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 637575.0,
      "end_time": 639220.0,
      "text": "have been built with rammed earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 639244.0,
      "end_time": 641537.0,
      "text": "but it's getting replaced by concrete."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 642231.0,
      "end_time": 645705.0,
      "text": "And this trend is happening very fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 645729.0,
      "end_time": 648705.0,
      "text": "Within only a couple of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 648729.0,
      "end_time": 651722.0,
      "text": "China has consumed more cement than the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 651746.0,
      "end_time": 653982.0,
      "text": "in the entire 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 654438.0,
      "end_time": 657947.0,
      "text": "And this trend of replacing natural building materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 657971.0,
      "end_time": 660224.0,
      "text": "with materials that require a lot of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 660248.0,
      "end_time": 662340.0,
      "text": "that are energy-intensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 662580.0,
      "end_time": 664990.0,
      "text": "and that emit CO2"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 664123.0,
      "end_time": 667463.0,
      "text": "is really clearly contributing to climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 667487.0,
      "end_time": 668900.0,
      "text": "And we have alternatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 668924.0,
      "end_time": 673175.0,
      "text": "such as mud, stones, timber, bamboo, earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 673199.0,
      "end_time": 677870.0,
      "text": "that are totally effective options for all sorts of purposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 677746.0,
      "end_time": 680293.0,
      "text": "This, for example, is an office building that we did"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 680317.0,
      "end_time": 682698.0,
      "text": "for Omicron Electronics in Austria."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 682722.0,
      "end_time": 685619.0,
      "text": "Mud is healthy for the planet, but also for the human bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 685643.0,
      "end_time": 688285.0,
      "text": "and the material is low-tech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 688309.0,
      "end_time": 690531.0,
      "text": "but the performance is high-tech."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 690556.0,
      "end_time": 694635.0,
      "text": "The earth walls keep the highly sophisticated tools in the building safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 694659.0,
      "end_time": 696569.0,
      "text": "by naturally regulating moisture."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 697410.0,
      "end_time": 700921.0,
      "text": "And this wall in my own home"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 700946.0,
      "end_time": 702374.0,
      "text": "is our humidfier."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 704192.0,
      "end_time": 707122.0,
      "text": "We love our six tons of dirt at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 707146.0,
      "end_time": 709636.0,
      "text": "not only because it's healthy and sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 710217.0,
      "end_time": 713273.0,
      "text": "Its archaic warmth is touching deep within."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 714528.0,
      "end_time": 719250.0,
      "text": "My personal dream is to build a mud skyscraper right in Manhattan."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 719640.0,
      "end_time": 721679.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 721703.0,
      "end_time": 722853.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 722878.0,
      "end_time": 725770.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 725101.0,
      "end_time": 726650.0,
      "text": "And this dream isn't so crazy"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 726674.0,
      "end_time": 728866.0,
      "text": "if you think of the mud city of Shibam in Yemen"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 728890.0,
      "end_time": 730755.0,
      "text": "that was built in the 16th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 730779.0,
      "end_time": 734470.0,
      "text": "and has lasted now for 500 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 735870.0,
      "end_time": 739194.0,
      "text": "What was possible that long ago is possible today as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 739218.0,
      "end_time": 742822.0,
      "text": "and we can apply all our technical know-how"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 742846.0,
      "end_time": 744856.0,
      "text": "to these ancient materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 744880.0,
      "end_time": 748482.0,
      "text": "so that it meets our needs and our dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 750223.0,
      "end_time": 752970.0,
      "text": "All around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752121.0,
      "end_time": 753872.0,
      "text": "and just below our feet ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 754880.0,
      "end_time": 757647.0,
      "text": "are wonderful natural building materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 757671.0,
      "end_time": 759460.0,
      "text": "Let's use them."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 760410.0,
      "end_time": 761957.0,
      "text": "And I deeply believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 761981.0,
      "end_time": 764734.0,
      "text": "our homes, our work spaces, our cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 765536.0,
      "end_time": 768114.0,
      "text": "would become more healthy and sustainable"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 769360.0,
      "end_time": 770582.0,
      "text": "and more humane"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 771907.0,
      "end_time": 773113.0,
      "text": "and beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 773752.0,
      "end_time": 774902.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 774927.0,
      "end_time": 779970.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}